data.description: Located on the 9th floor for immediate move in. The bedroom is spacious and carpeted with ample closet space. There are new light fixtures added by eating area. Unit is freshly painted. A private storage cage is also included. The building features a rooftop deck with stunning views of the lake and city, doorman, exercise facility, game room and laundry on site. Located less than a half mile from Argyle CTA Red Line. Express Bus Pickup is also in close proximity. There are rental parking options nearby for $125/mo. to $150/mo.
